<br>
Group slot 6: Misc. damage. Ideally another rogue, a monk, or our usual necro with Dire Charm. All are great choices.<br>
<br>
Important note: I would not advocate group efficiency over fun. I'm the biggest supporter of varied groups, doing things that you shouldn't be able to, with the weirdest classes.<br>
<br>
